{"tid":1374294,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］推，好重要，警犬濫權，要人手置頂","createTime":"2019-07-27T17:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T18:54:49.000Z","uid":2174,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4b0037c68ce278680c961854f228b54da8e769e0","tid":1374294,"uid":2174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:57:01.000Z","msg":"Sorry迫咗你地禁入嚟睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FrBBAk3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFrBBAk3.png&h=bd806776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日3點，上環遮打集會<br />\n追究警暴，追究今日同上星期血洗元朗站<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cefQVf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cefQVf.png&h=e4499441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同時唔好忘記我地嘅五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.完全撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2.撤回所有示威活動暴動定義<br />\n3.撤回所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會徹查警察濫權<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n雖然遊行不獲批，但我地唔好理繼續塞爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日有咁多人係元朗堅持<br />\n我地更加唔可以放棄<br />\n好重要，希望幫手推！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"0fa00f8efb7a8b91fc6c0db0081c4852371eb481","tid":1374294,"uid":73826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:58:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7120a97b41d26b94c8fb52f97146fcac12220f28","tid":1374294,"uid":2174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:58:59.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n下午三點 不見不散"},{"pid":"7d95742925cf79a392b797579c87e36588ac7941","tid":1374294,"uid":2174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:00:07.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n下午三點 不見不散"},{"pid":"008be6271fd061e63ee6b54d6ab261a32b43adc1","tid":1374294,"uid":2174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:01:18.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n下午三點 不見不散"},{"pid":"6b8e5b84c689544ef56f3762fecf02d453403672","tid":1374294,"uid":2174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime